  <feedback condition="$ans1.creditAchieved = 1">$correctFeedback</feedback>

<!--*********************************************
            Solution
**********************************************-->  
<solution>

  <ul>
    <li>Expand and simplify the original expression,
      <me><math>$expr = cos^2(theta) - 2 sin(theta)cos(theta) + sin^2(theta)</math></me>
    </li>
    <li>Now, notice that we can gather terms and simplify one step further, since <math>sin^2(theta) + cos^2(theta) = 1</math>,
      <me><math>$expr = -2 sin(theta)cos(theta) + 1</math></me>
    </li>
  </ul>
 
</solution>
</problem>
